This spectacular live concert, filmed at London s O2 using the latest
Ultra High Definition 4K technology, captures Peter Gabriel s celebration
of the 25th anniversary of his landmark album So . To mark the event
Gabriel reunited his original So touring band from 1986/87 and for the
very first time fans saw them play the multi-platinum selling album in
its entirety. Whilst the core of the performance is the So album, there
is so much more to the concert with unfinished, previously unreleased and
re-imagined songs sitting effortlessly alongside classic hits reflecting
what a multi-dimensional artist Peter Gabriel is. With innovative lighting
and staging, Back To Front offers a visual and narrative feast that puts
the viewer inside a concert like never before
